description: Located on the streets of Baltimore, Gypsy Queen Cafe on wheels marries inventive cuisine and cheeky-smart ass street food from the Executive chefs and co-owner's of Helen's Garden Restaurant (as seen on The FoodNetwork's CHEFSvsCITY). Our menu changes regularly and we have daily specials. Enjoy dining al fresco all year long! We're fast and friendly and easy to find. Ask about having us pull the truck up for your next special occasion (you would be so cool). Food Trucks Rock!
name: Gypsy Queen Cafe
